@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Help";
}

<section class="help-section">
    <h1>🆘 Help & Support</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Help section of the Student - Course Registration System! Here you can find useful tips and answers to common questions.</p>

    <h2>Getting Started 🚀</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To register for courses, navigate to the <strong>Students</strong> page and fill in your information.</li>
        <li>Teachers can manage their classes from the <strong>Teachers</strong> page.</li>
        <li>Administrators have access to advanced options for managing courses and users.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Troubleshooting 🔧</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>If you encounter login issues, try resetting your password or contact your administrator.</li>
        <li>Ensure your browser supports modern web standards (Chrome, Firefox, Edge recommended).</li>
        <li>For technical issues, please email support@lessons.com.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us 📞</h2>
    <p>If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@lessons.com">support@lessons.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: +1-234-567-890</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Thank you for using our system! 💜</p>
</section>

